ifthere was foul play involved?

578
00:28:14,573 --> 00:28:16,905
Give me a moment.

579
00:28:27,786 --> 00:28:29,879
You think the boy really did it?

580
00:28:29,988 --> 00:28:31,819
No.

581
00:28:31,923 --> 00:28:33,584
Why not?

582
00:28:33,692 --> 00:28:35,626
I was raised a Catholic

583
00:28:35,694 --> 00:28:39,824
