attorneywere present...

631
00:31:12,050 --> 00:31:14,450
Whatever. No.

632
00:31:14,519 --> 00:31:18,319
I put a call in to Sheriff Daniels.
He's on his way down here.

633
00:31:18,390 --> 00:31:23,453
- I'm going to ask him to releaseyou.
- Why areyou doing this?

634
00:31:23,562 --> 00:31:25,189
You were there, man.

635
00:31:25,297 --> 00:31:26,992
You saw foryourself.

636
00:31:27,098 --> 00:31:29,794
Did you poison Margaret Hohman?

637
00:31:29,868 --> 00:31:31,836
