638
00:31:31,903 --> 00:31:34,303
Did you poison her
using potassium or sodium cyanide?

639
00:31:34,372 --> 00:31:35,999
Because that's what killed her.

640
00:31:36,074 --> 00:31:37,803
What areyou talking about?

641
00:31:37,876 --> 00:31:41,277
You're innocent, Samuel.

642
00:31:41,346 --> 00:31:45,146
Unless you had a hand in
administering it. I don't thinkyou did.

643
00:31:45,217 --> 00:31:49,085
Whatever the cause, Mr. Mulder,
I am responsible.

644
00:31:49,154 --> 00:31:51,054
Evidence will be presented tomorrow.

645
00:31:51,122 --> 00:31:53,283
Habeas corpus law
will force them to releaseyou.

646
00:31:53,358 --> 00:31:54,825
You should go home
and get some rest.

647
00:31:54,926 --> 00:31:57,087
just leave me alone, okay?

648
00:31:57,195 --> 00:31:59,663
Ifyou think the punishment
foryour sins

649
00:31:59,731 --> 00:32:01,665
is the deaths ofthose people...

650
00:32:01,733 --> 00:32:04,201
The Lord has testified against me.

651
00:32:04,269 --> 00:32:07,329
I can't stand here and argue
with your biblical rhetoric

652
00:32:07,405 --> 00:32:09,965
but I do know that the law
will find you innocent.

653
00:32:17,048 --> 00:32:21,508
You said you could see my pain.

654
00:32:21,586 --> 00:32:22,518
Look at me.

655
00:32:26,458 --> 00:32:27,720
What doyou see now?

656
00:32:27,826 --> 00:32:30,693
I see nothing.

657
00:32:31,763 --> 00:32:34,323
I am blind.

658
00:32:34,432 --> 00:32:36,059
I don't believeyou.

659
00:32:36,134 --> 00:32:37,761
I've seen her.

660
00:32:37,836 --> 00:32:40,361
It was her, wasn't it?

661
00:32:40,438 --> 00:32:42,235
Your sister?

662
00:32:42,307 --> 00:32:44,400
You made her appear to me,
didn'tyou?

663
00:32:46,478 --> 00:32:47,410
Look at me.

664
00:32:47,479 --> 00:32:49,709
I am very tired, Mr. Mulder.

665
00:32:49,781 --> 00:32:51,146
Is she alive?!

666
00:32:51,216 --> 00:32:54,014
Is that what I'm supposed
to believe

667
00:32:54,085 --> 00:32:55,780
or is this a trick?

668
00:32:55,854 --> 00:32:57,719
You mean...

669
00:32:57,789 --> 00:33:01,225
a trick ofthe devil?

670
00:33:01,293 --> 00:33:03,761
(exasperated sigh)

671
00:33:03,828 --> 00:33:06,228
jailer!

672
