His innocence.

676
00:33:29,487 --> 00:33:31,978
Aren'tyou out ofyour depth here?

677
00:33:32,057 --> 00:33:34,184
This may be Hicksville toyou

678
00:33:34,292 --> 00:33:36,283
but we do try and hew
to the legal system.

679
00:33:36,394 --> 00:33:39,056
He seems determined
to stay here anyway.

680
00:33:39,164 --> 00:33:41,598
What does that tell you?

681
00:33:41,666 --> 00:33:43,497
It tells meyou're determined
to have him charged

682
00:33:43,568 --> 00:33:47,060
whileyour real homicide suspect
is still at large.

683
00:33:51,976 --> 00:33:54,274
(footsteps)

