I'll get it.

689
00:34:44,462 --> 00:34:46,362
I'll get it.

690
00:34:53,304 --> 00:34:55,431
Ma'am, Sheriff.

691
00:34:55,507 --> 00:34:57,532
Hey, Dennis. How areya?

692
00:34:57,609 --> 00:35:00,407
just fine, ma'am,just fine.

693
00:35:00,478 --> 00:35:02,571
Except we had an incident
down at thejail.

694
00:35:02,647 --> 00:35:04,171
What incident, Tyson?

695
00:35:04,249 --> 00:35:06,547
The preacher boy.

696
00:35:06,618 --> 00:35:08,586
He's dead.

697
00:35:17,028 --> 00:35:19,496
