702
00:35:28,106 --> 00:35:31,906
Died before the ambulance got here.

703
00:35:31,976 --> 00:35:33,341
His blood is spilled

704
00:35:33,411 --> 00:35:34,935
and it's all overyou!

705
00:35:35,013 --> 00:35:36,105
Reverend...

706
00:35:40,218 --> 00:35:41,412
How much longer

