710
00:35:47,959 --> 00:35:50,120
Reverend Hartley...

711
00:35:52,664 --> 00:35:54,154
we're sorry foryour loss.

712
00:35:54,265 --> 00:35:58,565
That boy... he was blessed.

713
00:35:58,636 --> 00:36:00,627
He never hurt a soul.

714
00:36:00,705 --> 00:36:01,797
