722
00:36:20,658 --> 00:36:22,091
The kind when you've
forgotten your keys

723
00:36:22,193 --> 00:36:23,626
and you're trying
to figure out

724
00:36:23,695 --> 00:36:24,719
how to get back
in the house.

725
00:36:32,403 --> 00:36:34,769
What exactly
are we trying to find?

726
00:36:34,839 --> 00:36:36,101
Clues.

727
00:36:36,174 --> 00:36:37,971
Oh.

728
00:36:54,259 --> 00:36:56,250
What does it mean?

729
00:36:59,864 --> 00:37:01,559
Mulder: Let's find out.

730
00:37:12,911 --> 00:37:14,708
Scully.

731
00:37:16,414 --> 00:37:18,541
It's potato.

732
00:37:20,351 --> 00:37:22,148
Someone left a trail offood

733
