754
00:38:43,034 --> 00:38:45,901
You call this life?!

755
00:38:48,373 --> 00:38:49,931
(knocking)

756
00:38:52,477 --> 00:38:54,377
What in tarnation doyou want?

757
00:38:54,445 --> 00:38:55,605
We have a warrant

758
00:38:55,680 --> 00:38:57,671
for the arrest of Leonard Vance.

759
00:38:57,749 --> 00:38:58,909
Where is he?

760
00:38:58,983 --> 00:39:00,041
You must be mistaken.

761
00:39:00,118 --> 00:39:02,018
Scully: Afraid not, Reverend.

762
00:39:02,086 --> 00:39:04,020
We traced
a pesticide order to him

763
00:39:04,088 --> 00:39:05,555
from a chemical company.

764
00:39:05,623 --> 00:39:06,715
Cyanogen bromide--

765
00:39:06,791 --> 00:39:08,554
It's a cyanide derivative.

766
00:39:08,660 --> 00:39:11,857
Leonard poisoned those people?

767
00:39:11,963 --> 00:39:14,454
(whimpering)

768
00:39:18,803 --> 00:39:20,532
Getyour clothes on, Vance.

769
00:39:20,605 --> 00:39:22,038
You're under arrest.

770
00:39:22,106 --> 00:39:24,336
I betrayed him.

771
00:39:25,777 --> 00:39:27,210
Cyanide.

772
