to the hospital ourselves.

775
00:39:34,719 --> 00:39:37,984
I thought,
"Why didn't he let me die?"

776
00:39:38,056 --> 00:39:39,683
Beware offalse prophets

777
00:39:39,757 --> 00:39:42,089
who come toyou
in sheep's clothing

778
00:39:42,193 --> 00:39:46,152
but inwardly
are ravening wolves.

779
00:39:46,264 --> 00:39:48,459
That's what I thought he was

780
00:39:48,533 --> 00:39:51,161
because who else would bring me back

781
00:39:51,235 --> 00:39:53,538
Iooking like this?

782
00:39:53,671 --> 00:39:55,798
He was here.

783
00:39:55,873 --> 00:39:58,398
- Who?
